Johnny Mack Brown https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Johnny_Mack_Brown 0 Johnny "Mack" Brown (September 1, 1904 – November 14, 1974) was an American college football player and film actor originally billed as John Mack Brown at the height of his screen career. He was mostly in Western films.
